parameters.name: query
parameters.value: SELECT mh.hash, pc.contactvalue FROM public.messagehash mh JOIN app.menu_data md ON (md.uuid01 = '14ec8e33-961a-4a62-9fe7-869ca9e12a4b'::uuid AND md.datatype IN ('message', 'encounterEvent') AND md.id = mh.message_id) JOIN pkbperson p ON p.defaultaccountid = md.account_id JOIN personcontact pc ON (p.id = pc.person_id AND pc.contacttype = 'EMAIL' AND pc.confirmed = true) ORDER BY mh.hash, pc.contactvalue
